== Honours ==

Greek South Division Championship (once) : 1934-1935

National League Topscorer (once) : 1935-1936 (12 goals)

Champion of Romania (three times) : [[Divizia A 1936-37|1936-1937]], [[Divizia A 1938-39|1938-1939]], [[Divizia A 1939-40|1939-1940]]

